{"tid":726333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大摩：林鄭新六招不太可能壓抑樓價","createTime":"2018-07-02T09:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T10:18:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b581246815aea92e485ec7501895339bd6da2572","tid":726333,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00002/1530506404533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00002%2F1530506404533&d=wJQDztqai%2BickeFlznggjQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b2a387ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00002%2F1530506404533&h=00497f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00002/1530506404533</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00002/7ce28398a849248f78ca470d00f48d1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00002%2F7ce28398a849248f78ca470d00f48d1e.jpg&h=676da31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥上周推出樓市新六招，摩根士丹利發表報告指，推出新六招以增加🇨🇳房地產🇨🇳供應的最新措施，包括當中增設的針對空置一手私人住宅單位徵收「額外差餉」，不大可能影響樓價；市場仍有6-9個月的時間來出售剩餘🇨🇳庫存🇨🇳。<br />\n<br />\n對發展商而言，大摩認為，🇨🇳庫存🇨🇳較多的新地(0016)、嘉里建設(0683)近期股價表現可能承壓。至於要求發展商每次推售的住宅單位數目，均不能少於有關預售樓花同意書所涵蓋的住宅單位總數20%，此舉對供應沒有太大影響。"},{"pid":"188b7dfacbc869c45f9cc10383ba83287d20ae3a","tid":726333,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28c690c95d65f542a51ecc70cde15926beda4294","tid":726333,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"大摩吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買開股票知咩事啦"},{"pid":"0ec0f555b3014bb1204955df868dc99f142a0cda","tid":726333,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,